{"tid":1891502,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光：「係人都戴口罩就唔掂啦，你見我都冇戴」","createTime":"2020-02-22T01:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T09:57:58.000Z","uid":212626,"like":17,"dislike":177,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"cf3fb226af971ea32be510b1940f2eaa8355a695","tid":1891502,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T01:35:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>「係人都戴口罩就唔掂」</strong><br />\n<br />\n統計處日前公布，去年11月至今年1月經季節調整的失業率為3.4%，較去年10至12月升0.1個百分點。羅估計在疫情之下，預期失業率將難免升至4%至5%，「作為政府官員，我唔想估計」，至於是否再攀升視乎疫情是否能迅速受控。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光又重申，<span style=\"color: red;\">「係人都戴口罩就唔掂」，使用量追不上產量：「你見我唔戴，每次我都輕描淡寫引述世衞講，冇病嘅人唔使戴」</span>。他指香港每周耗用5,000萬個口罩，日用700萬個，「反而好多有病嘅人就唔戴」。對於被指22日不戴口罩之言論離地，羅稱：「我明白社會嘅睇法，我自己嘅睇法就係咁。你可以避免去人多地方、減少社會接觸，可以唔使戴就唔戴。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200222/HS3DTJXPVHWJ7SKUFCMOZWZI3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200222%2FHS3DTJXPVHWJ7SKUFCMOZWZI3U%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAI429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=b77d9fec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200222%2FHS3DTJXPVHWJ7SKUFCMOZWZI3U%2F&h=2dd04728\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200222/HS3DTJXPVHWJ7SKUFCMOZWZI3U/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIQ160嘅邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454a51d9e8e3511279875f307c18d253fe8bae9a","tid":1891502,"uid":191633,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T01:38:47.000Z","msg":"有幾撚唔掂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔戴hi咗野就最掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9cf8c67caf18b644e758f820e672d3c4bfbde9","tid":1891502,"uid":216441,"like":99,"dislike":1,"score":98,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T01:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6O6JgZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu